{"tid":2305100,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【蝗蟲搞鬼】Netflix限制「土耳其」付款賬戶在「香港」 水網絡觀看","createTime":"2020-11-29T10:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T12:53:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21676789c36f5964920769b36c405c1cd423b808","tid":2305100,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:49:01.000Z","msg":"今天正常打開Netflix的時候，提示「您的帳戶無法在此地點使用」，錯誤代碼是 D7111-1331，網頁app以及windows的客戶端都出現了，經過咨詢客服告知：新上線了檢查帳戶支付區域與觀看區域的ip檢測，目前應該是只針對支付區域是「土耳其」並且觀看區域是「香港」，兩個條件同時成立，會出現這個問題。<br />\n  目前還不知道會不會進一步擴大檢測，比如擴大到「阿根廷」付款賬戶。 目前土耳其是世界第一低價區，阿根廷為第二。所以合租&amp;商家為了極限壓價是肯定選擇土耳其的。 目前已知「土耳其&rdquo;賬戶在非「香港」網絡下還正常，不確定是否進一步擴大檢測。"},{"pid":"5d9884092b39a41c7b308eea613f3ecfca56bad6","tid":2305100,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c22875b164851574a3b58f244a4ecb38e7469b","tid":2305100,"uid":8918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:44:20.000Z","msg":"好撚心正正經經比正價光明正大睇啦<br />\n幾個人share已經好平<br />\n仲要走精面慳果少少"},{"pid":"4a916441822063b26732e53ec02c4f37d9af2e05","tid":2305100,"uid":10014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:50:13.000Z","msg":"Google drive 同 Yourube premier 用印度果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c15743f8b25d13b896cccd7354aa9443ff823c","tid":2305100,"uid":15984,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:53:42.000Z","msg":"iphone4 年代上淘寶人仔200$ 買土耳其itunes acc 入面有3000 美金<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用到而家"}]}